Nicholas Aberle: Assignment 3
Time to complete: 3 hours

Compile using:
  qmake
  make
Run using:
  ./hw03
Actions:
  Drag top slider to change theta angle of the cube
  Drag second slider to change phi angle of the cube
  Drag third slider to change size of the cube
      + Note procedural texture remains correctly scaled
  Enter a number in first text field and it will automatically be multiplied and displayed in the next field (only numbers 0-100 are allowed)
  Click party on/off radio buttons to turn party mode on! (Cube side colors are randomized using a timer function)
      + When the shader is enabled, the colors will change
  Click "Toggle shaders!" button to turn procedural texture shader on or off (on by default)
